#about_me

	.col-md-12.about-me-details

		.about-me-mission
			.about-me-header 
				I always seek adventure.
			.about-me-subtitle
				I fuck up a lot, and sometimes succeed too; but the journey's always worthwhile.
			.about-me-mission-text
				“Adventure” is aggressively overused, so let me clarify...I thrive most when uncertainty exists, the unexpected is expected and “new” describes everyone I meet, everywhere I go and the situations I experience.
				<br>
				<br>
				I've learned that travel and business are very aligned and I view them as such. My affinity for adventure branches to both of my passions: in business, it’s those who are comfortable deviating from the norm that will succeed and in travel, it’s those who go outside of their comfort zone that will have the most authentic experiences.
				<br>
				<br>
				Whether through launching travel tech companies, riding across countries on motorcycles, learning to code or circumnaviating the world on a ship, I'm constantly striving towards adventures in unfamiliar people, places and experiences.

